{"tid":2219688,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳弘毅：法庭須解釋國安法","createTime":"2020-09-27T05:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T07:11:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7831caaf1cd7f658b6f6571349168929e4965bb","tid":2219688,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/PTVASVIBWRH7FEWYIZW74DEYH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FPTVASVIBWRH7FEWYIZW74DEYH4%2F&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0gV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=325c6c65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FPTVASVIBWRH7FEWYIZW74DEYH4%2F&h=41e4ef68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/PTVASVIBWRH7FEWYIZW74DEYH4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陳弘毅：法庭須解釋國安法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PrGWN3IH-DVeVXpUqdEEuyVwPJg=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5FBIWZ77BJBWPJRWIXGNSCE4VA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPrGWN3IH-DVeVXpUqdEEuyVwPJg%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5FBIWZ77BJBWPJRWIXGNSCE4VA.jpg&h=e3c5104b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法實施三個多月，被控違反國安法的小市民越來越多。基本法委員會委員陳弘毅（圖）昨日指，若警方和律政司將國安法的範圍演繹得較廣，就有更多案件交上法庭，而法庭就有更大責任去解釋法律，不過他相信，法院會按普通法和國際人權標準解釋國安法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：與黨友周浩鼎葛珮帆唱反調  曾鈺成「量刑委會礙司法獨立」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料以普通法為標準<br />\n<br />\n陳弘毅出席港大有關國安法的網上論壇時稱，法庭審理案件前，是需由警方調查、律政司檢控，若警方和律政司將國安法演繹得較廣，便會有很多個案交上法庭審理，而法庭就有更大責任處理，包括解釋法律。但陳相信，法庭日後會按普通法和國際人權標準解釋國安法。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，中央之所以實施港版國安法，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳弘毅又認為，港版國安法難以解決港人身份認同的問題。他以政府押後今屆立法會選舉為例，形容即使選舉押後一年，選民仍。。。。。。。。。。。。望能以國安法為香港一國兩制定下底線，強調「一國」的重要性。"},{"pid":"d858e0692faa68ec82aeea4366b2baadc0d0097b","tid":2219688,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"又係呢個陰聲陰氣奶共狗"},{"pid":"55945a2f8c32ee38060b0c1e8cd1fdc8e19ce273","tid":2219688,"uid":126317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"法律界癌細胞<br />\n佢上面有白頭婆<br />\n下面有湯渣，大波驊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cc8f6d6a25992e6c81fabb45fd2d07ce88d3d7","tid":2219688,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"交上支那法庭？"},{"pid":"b119f37a13c86862b87d6d41c0d1eb6ceacd5bf3","tid":2219688,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"陳匪弘毅又出黎叫人信司法<br />\n食屎啦"},{"pid":"e276a5ce4b45df320c03fb7a84b3abdaafb711e2","tid":2219688,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"原來法庭可以解釋國安法<br />\n乜唔係淨係得共產黨先解釋到架咩"},{"pid":"fe91510cfd469bab4d7aa89df61d3e29dc32f261","tid":2219688,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係好事黎咩？<br />\n解釋前做乜都可以係分裂國家<br />\n解釋後可能得幾個行為先叫分裂國家"},{"pid":"90c5ca51cb6564f2e74441589d0a6cebfde46dce","tid":2219688,"uid":235754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe91510cfd469bab4d7aa89df61d3e29dc32f261","tid":2219688,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係好事黎咩？<br />\n解釋前做乜都可以係分裂國家<br />\n解釋後可能得幾個行為先叫分裂國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"因為共慘黨永遠講一套做一套 佢話唔會佢咪一樣會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23339651d0a574826498bdb31130ae7b181346c","tid":2219688,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦，解完又點"},{"pid":"1281ee711528b083